{"tid":235768,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解會有咁多人擁護資本主義","createTime":"2017-05-09T08:54:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T15:43:29.000Z","uid":55874,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c9b636883b0a68e798c6d0d8c82c9c7dc2e4011","tid":235768,"uid":55874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:54:33.000Z","msg":"明明自己都係資本主義嘅失敗者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對啲大商家就話人地都要做生意要搵食<br />\n對住獨立組織就話無錢學咩人乜乜乜<br />\n資本商業社會就係咁云云<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚奇怪 平時又唔見咁包容你老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大財團食多你幾千萬就好撚體諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平民賺多五蚊都係極醜惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n根本大家窮撚<br />\n(唔好扮到你唔係 你比得上誠哥先講 <br />\n你再高人工都係打工仔)<br />\n好應該支持共產主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 共9班有錢契弟嘅產<br />\n所有嘢都要共享<br />\n一齊窮都好撚過得誠哥有錢我地做奴隸<br />\n共產萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支持共產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b1c52f56e16243f270f9f78a97cd6809b22b5bb","tid":235768,"uid":48362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:55:07.000Z","msg":"多重標準 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7557a683382785c5b39b8113b88477f87660ba1","tid":235768,"uid":82949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:57:02.000Z","msg":"all people are equal,<br />\nbut some people are more equal than others.<br />\n<br />\n--Animal Farm"},{"pid":"7bd969997c201d7537510b3ba4db0d0322b63b17","tid":